<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1177591-i-read-the-first-book-in-the-series-about">I read the first book in the series about a decade ago and while I liked it I never got around to the second book in the series. Should I go back and read the first book before starting the Fall of Hyperion or is it okay to jump into the second book with Hyperion barely in my memory?</a>
</div>
